{"parentUuid":"65111dda-1ac3-4a5e-85f0-c24f3dd37e85","isSidechain":false,"userType":"external","cwd":"C:\\Users\\Administrator","sessionId":"d3e43671-6460-4ad8-8d09-6cd3cd29c944","version":"2.1.59","gitBranch":"HEAD","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01836a6gUGBtqVhZGh3VkqV5","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking about how to connect to Windows desktop without a password. This could be about:\n1. Windows Remote Desktop (RDP) without password\n2. Windows login without password\n3. Some other type of connection\n\nLet me think about this - this is a legitimate administrative/IT question. I'll provide information about common methods for passwordless Windows desktop access.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":3,"cache_creation_input_tokens":28574,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":28574},"output_tokens":0,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"}},"requestId":"req_011CYW57GD7sctm3EMLLc3hV","type":"assistant","uuid":"813b181c-8313-405f-a261-0a7f756ca5b3","timestamp":"2026-02-26T04:45:20.737Z"}
{"parentUuid":"813b181c-8313-405f-a261-0a7f756ca5b3","isSidechain":false,"userType":"external","cwd":"C:\\Users\\Administrator","sessionId":"d3e43671-6460-4ad8-8d09-6cd3cd29c944","version":"2.1.59","gitBranch":"HEAD","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01836a6gUGBtqVhZGh3VkqV5","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Windows 데스크탑 연결(RDP) 패스워드 없이 접속하는 방법입니다.\n\n## 방법 1: 빈 패스워드 계정 허용 (로컬 정책)\n\n기본적으로 Windows는 빈 패스워드 계정의 RDP 접속을 차단합니다. 이를 허용하려면:\n\n```\ngpedit.msc → 컴퓨터 구성 → Windows 설정 → 보안 설정\n→ 로컬 정책 → 보안 옵션\n→ \"콘솔 로그온만 허용하도록 빈 암호 사용 계정 제한\" → 사용 안 함\n```\n\n## 방법 2: 자격증명 저장 (클라이언트 측)\n\n연결하는 PC에서:\n```\ncmdkey /generic:TERMSRV/192.168.x.x /user:Administrator /pass:패스워드\n```\n이후 RDP 연결 시 자동 로그인됩니다.\n\n## 방법 3: RDP 파일에 저장\n\n`.rdp` 파일에:\n```\nusername:s:Administrator\npassword 51:b:암호화된값\n```\n`mstsc /v:IP /admin` 로 저장된 자격증명으로 접속.\n\n## 방법 4: SSH 터널 + 키 인증\n\n패스워드 대신 SSH 키 기반 인증 후 RDP 포워딩:\n```bash\nssh -L 3389:localhost:3389 user@서버IP\n# 이후 localhost:3389 로 RDP 접속\n```\n\n---\n\n**어떤 상황인지** 알려주시면 더 정확한 방법을 안내드립니다:\n- 원격에서 RDP 접속?\n- 로컬 PC 자동 로그인?\n- 특정 계정/버전?"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":3,"cache_creation_input_tokens":28574,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":642,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":28574,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"requestId":"req_011CYW57GD7sctm3EMLLc3hV","type":"assistant","uuid":"3d0a1963-8896-4e56-b53e-2ed00be1b1ad","timestamp":"2026-02-26T04:45:30.773Z"}
